From 2bbe90f5997860ef182e57d809fce4e099c0cd1a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 11:49:20 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Exp 1: Replace ghost title defaults with surfer
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Empty/fallback titles and titlebar chrome use 🏄 / 🏄 TermSurf
instead of 👻 / 👻 Ghostty. Theme preview CLI aligned.
